
Run C or C++ directly from the terminal


How to.. 
 1. Download the script
 2. Put the script where you want to be. [Preferably in the path where your c or c++ code resides]
 3. After typing your C or C++ code file save it.
 4. Now on terminal type 
        ./run.sh [filename]
 5. It will compile and run the code.
 
Note.
 1. Remember to type the full file name
 2. case sensitive.
